dc_title_s: Iberian Peninsula 1:250,000: Pontevedra, sheet 10. Series A.M.S. M581
dc_description_s: United States. Army Map Service. North Decimal Degree 43.0000. South Decimal Degree 42.0000. East Decimal Degree -8.0000. West Decimal Degree -9.0000. Alternate title: Pontevedra, Spain. Polyconic projection. With Spanish-English glossary. Relief shown by 100 m. contour interval, gradient tint and spot heights. Standard map series designation: A.M.S. M581. "Compiled from Portugal, 1:50,000, Services Geodesicos, 1935; Spain, 1:100,000, Estade Mayor del Ejercite, sheets 22, 42, 1915, 1919; Iberian Peninsula, 1:250,000, Geographical Section, General Staff, 1941, sheets S. 1272, 1280, 2472, 2480; Road Map of Spain and Portugal, 1:1,500,000, G.S.G.S., 1941, corrected from intelligence Reports, 1942-44. Partially revised from aerial photography 1942-43.".
